    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"long term benefit\" feels pretty vague when i'm looking at my actual payroll for next month. it sounds like you're prioritizing the \"idea\" of a better economy over the reality of a business owner actually staying afloat. can you just be straight with me—is the consensus actually that these hikes are good for the economy, or is that just what people say to avoid talking about how much they hurt small business owners?",
